dow, which includes a bowl and street structures, perhaps without the 3m vert ramp which few can use.\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3474, \"end\": 3478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"score\": 0.9999999999336069, \"rank\": 6.418778593748227e-11, \"text\": \"Toby\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\"}, {\"begin\": 3515, \"end\": 3527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fairy_Meadow,_New_South_Wales\", \"score\": 0.9999995963244961, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fairy Meadow\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fairy_Meadow,_New_South_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fairy_Meadow,_New_South_Wales\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"simple - a park\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"a bowl and street structures\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"the 3m vert ramp\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would not mind if there was one in yesterday,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"yesterday\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flic, a student at Holy Spirit, said people should not worry about bad behaviour.\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Flic\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3691}, {\"ngram\": \"a student\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3702}, {\"ngram\": \"Holy Spirit\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3717}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"bad behaviour\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me growing up, I pretty much lived at the skate park,\\\" said.\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the skate park\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember just coming home from school and I would skate down to the skate park and I would not even have to message anyone - I would just know all my mates would be there and at a young age it was just the best.\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 4051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3877}, {\"ngram\": \"the skate park\", \"from\": 3904, \"to\": 3918}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 3962}, {\"ngram\": \"all my mates\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3995}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 4018, \"to\": 4029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of stereotypes around skaters, but I think once you are part of the community, you can see how welcoming everyone is, and it's really fun being able to hang at skate park with all your mates.\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4068}, {\"ngram\": \"stereotypes\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4083}, {\"ngram\": \"skaters\", \"from\": 4091, \"to\": 4098}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 4133, \"to\": 4146}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4182}, {\"ngram\": \"skate park\", \"from\": 4229, \"to\": 4239}, {\"ngram\": \"all your mates\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It creates a place for the younger people in the community, like a safe space where they can feel they can hang out apart from home, apart from school, another place for them to hang out and really enjoy themselves.\\\"\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 4274, \"to\": 4281}, {\"ngram\": \"the younger people\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4304}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4321}, {\"ngram\": \"a safe space\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4340}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 4390, \"to\": 4394}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Thirroul Village Committee (TVC) meeting on April 28 was told by councillor Richard Martin what they already knew - that the development of the skate park had been delayed by another year.\", \"from\": 4481, \"to\": 4673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4569, \"end\": 4575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9991753659304242, \"rank\": 0.0008253144737653576, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TVC\", \"from\": 4513, \"to\": 4516}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 4529, \"to\": 4534}, {\"ngram\": \"the development\", \"from\": 4606, \"to\": 4621}, {\"ngram\": \"the skate park\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4639}, {\"ngram\": \"another year\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two years ago thecity council saidthere was money allocated and design work would start in the 2022-23 financial year.\", \"from\": 4675, \"to\": 4793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 4719, \"to\": 4724}, {\"ngram\": \"design work\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4750}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022-23 financial year\", \"from\": 4766, \"to\": 4792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time TVC (then) vice-president Elliot Stein said the group had been \\\"promoting the idea of a skate park in Thirroul for over a decade and a half now\\\".\", \"from\": 4795, \"to\": 4952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4909, \"end\": 4917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thirroul_Butchers\", \"score\": 0.7708816688987261, \"rank\": 0.2972159545948942, \"text\": \"Thirroul\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thirroul_Butchers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thirroul_Butchers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 4798, \"to\": 4806}, {\"ngram\": \"TVC\", \"from\": 4807, \"to\": 4810}, {\"ngram\": \"vice\", \"from\": 4818, \"to\": 4822}, {\"